        "subject": "=You're paying ~${{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.scan.licenseWasteMonthly }}/mo for licenses nobody uses",
        "emailFormat": "text",
        "text": "=Hi {{ ($('Webhook').item.json.body.user.name || '').split(' ')[0] || 'there' }},\n\nYour scan flagged about ${{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.scan.licenseWasteMonthly }}/month in unused or never-signed-in licenses. That's money you can recover - usually more than the cost of fixing everything else combined.\n\nThe full report shows exactly which accounts and how to reclaim them:\nhttps://tenanthawk.io/dashboard/report\n\n- Tenant Hawk",
        "options": {}
