        "subject": "={{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.scan.expiringSoonCount }} things in your tenant are about to expire",
        "emailFormat": "text",
        "text": "=Hi {{ ($('Webhook').item.json.body.user.name || '').split(' ')[0] || 'there' }},\n\nApp secrets, SSO signing certs and domains don't fail gracefully - they take an integration or sign-in down with no warning. Your scan found {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.scan.expiringSoonCount }} expiring soon.\n\nSee each one, the days remaining, and how to rotate it before it fires:\nhttps://tenanthawk.io/dashboard/report\n\n- Tenant Hawk",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "send-a3",
      "name": "A3 - The time-bomb",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
